entry.title: Welcome!
entry.content:
My name is Nabeel Eledroos.

That’s me in the back left, working on a gesture controlled car at HackUMass.

I am currently a Junior Computer Science student UMass Amherst, interested in a wide variety of disciplines within computer science such as computer vision, cybersecurity, and embedded programming.

Take a look at my GitHub page to see a portfolio of projects that I have worked on. Please feel free to check out my LinkedIn as well as download my resume on the sidebar to the left.

Contact Me

You can email me at: nabeel@eledroos.net.
